HEADWORD: Whereinto
<hw>Where`in*to"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Into which; -- used relatively.</def>⟦br⟧
